{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"e99b7e60-04bb-4013-940c-8a215c00b9fe","content":"This template is **not quite ready** to publish. Here are the issues:\n\n**Missing required field:**\n- `$schema` — recommended for validation: `\"$schema\": \"http://json.schemastore.org/template\"`\n\n**Missing recommended fields:**\n- `groupIdentity` — needed if you plan multiple language/framework variants\n- `precedence` — important for version upgrades\n- `description` — NuGet gallery will show nothing useful without it\n- `defaultName` — controls the default project name (e.g., `\"WebApi1\"`)\n\n**Other concerns:**\n1. **No `preferNameDirectory`** — typically `true` for project templates\n2. **Placeholder identity/author** — `\"MyCompany.WebApi.CSharp\"` and `\"My Company\"` look like placeholders that should be replaced with real values before publishing\n3. **Framework symbol** — the `choices` field should use an array format in newer template engine versions; the object format still works but is legacy\n\n**Minimum fix to be publish-ready:** add a `description` field and replace the placeholder identity/author with real values. The rest are best practices.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f892214b-24b9-43d4-8a95-ca77fd9e95fd","outputTokens":261,"requestId":"AC2A:2CDF90:149DF9:19841C:69F54C0C"},"id":"ce628022-4247-4119-a6d5-49885dd06697","timestamp":"2026-05-02T00:57:56.717Z","parentId":"0bb4fb0b-437d-4800-8f81-21821a68c2b9"}
